    <body>
      <div type="transcription" xml:id="transcription_aad_0100" xml:lang="en">
        <div type="letter">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00329/" ed="1r" type="sheet"/>
          <div>
            <ab hand="#hand_gray_onb">
              <lb/>15|B 870<unclear>|3</unclear>
            </ab>
          </div>
          <div type="letter_message" hand="#type_cc_spiel">
            <opener>
              <dateline>
                <date>
                  <lb/><space quantity="25" unit="char"/>20th July 1972
                </date>
              </dateline>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Dear <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">Mr Auden</rs>,
              </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
              <lb/><space quantity="4" unit="char"/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_78">I</rs> am very glad the <rs type="lit_work" ref="#lit_work_id_225" ana="acdh:aad-transcript__0090.xml#ana_103">translations</rs> seem
              <lb/>good to you . If you want anything improved
              <lb/>when you have looked at them a bit more
              <lb/>closely, do let me know. Meanwhile would
              <lb/>you insert the word '<foreign xml:lang="de">Weinernten</foreign>' in the
              <lb/>empty spot in the last verse of <rs type="lit_work" ref="#lit_work_id_238">'Mezzo-
              <lb/>giorno'</rs>, and alter the two last lines of
              <lb/>the last verse but three of <rs type="lit_work" ref="#lit_work_id_236">'Freud'</rs> in the
              <lb/>following way :
              <seg xml:lang="de">
                <lb/><space quantity="5" unit="char"/>nicht nur,weil sie allein uns noch zum
                <lb/><space quantity="34" unit="char"/>Staunen
                <lb/><space quantity="1" unit="char"/>bewegen kann, sondern auch, etc.
              </seg>
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/><space quantity="4" unit="char"/>Of course I shall translate your <rs type="lit_work" ref="#lit_work_id_99">state-
              <lb/>ment</rs>, if you give me a week or two for it.
              <lb/>(I am <rs type="lit_work" ref="#lit_work_id_240">doing <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_283">Stoppard</rs>'s <rs type="lit_work" ref="#lit_work_id_239">'Jumpers'</rs></rs> at the
              <lb/>moment). How unpleasant for you. Have you
              <lb/>got a good chartered accountant? I know
              <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_282">Kreisky</rs>'s - perhaps he can help.
            </p>
            <closer>
              <salute>
                <lb/><space quantity="5" unit="char"/>Best regards,
              </salute>
              <salute>
                <lb/><space quantity="18" unit="char"/>Yours sincerely,
              </salute>
            </closer>
          </div>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00330/" ed="1v" type="sheet"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
